org.eclipse.scada.configuration.component.impl

Class SystemImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
      • org.eclipse.scada.configuration.component.impl.SystemImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    System

    public class SystemImpl
extends MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements System
    An implementation of the model object 'System'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Levels
    • Configurations
    • Services
    • Infrastructure
    • Default Customization Pipeline
    • Default Archive Selector
